OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1782917279
OL,3,CDigital and AI expert says changing
OL,4,Ccultural norms starts with social
OL,5,Cmedia ban
OL,7,FA digital and AI expert says the
OL,8,FChannel Islands should look at
OL,9,Ffollowing the UK's lead and introduce
OL,10,Fa social media ban for under-16s.
OL,12,FDr Kaitlyn Regehr has been in Jersey
OL,13,Fthis week to discuss her work, which
OL,14,Finvestigates the societal impact of
OL,15,Falgorithms and digital technologies.
OL,17,FHer team is also now working on the
OL,18,Fguidance to go alongside the
OL,19,Fimplementation and enforcement of the
OL,20,FUK's social media ban.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
