PN,35502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1782917279
OL,3,CDigital and AI expert says changing
OL,4,Ccultural norms starts with social
OL,5,Cmedia ban
OL,7,FShe says social media, technology, and
OL,8,Fartificial intelligence are not
OL,9,Finnately bad for children - however,
OL,10,Fthe algorithms which currently drive
OL,11,Fsocial media mean they have become
OL,12,Fnegative spaces.
OL,14,F"The problem is the way in which
OL,15,Fsocial media is currently structured
OL,16,Fis prioritising hate, harm, and
OL,17,Fdisinformation - because it's more
OL,18,Fattention-grabbing", she told ITV News.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1782917279
OL,3,CDigital and AI expert says changing
OL,4,Ccultural norms starts with social
OL,5,Cmedia ban
OL,7,F"And because we've allowed that system
OL,8,Fto take place, it's no longer a safe
OL,9,Fspace for young people. "
OL,11,FDr Regehr adds the introduction of a
OL,12,Fsocial media ban is just the first
OL,13,Fstep on the road towards creating
OL,14,Flasting cultural change.
OL,16,F"This is not about one quick-and easy
OL,17,Ffix", she explains.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1782917279
OL,3,CDigital and AI expert says changing
OL,4,Ccultural norms starts with social
OL,5,Cmedia ban
OL,7,F"This is about changing cultural norms
OL,8,Faround harm and consumption - and I
OL,9,Fthink what we'll do is see a slow
OL,10,Fshift around the cultural
OL,11,Facceptability of the stronghold that
OL,12,Ftechnology now has around childhood."
OL,14,FDr Regehr says many of the parents she
OL,15,Fhas spoken with say they are concerned
OL,16,Fabout balancing this regulation of
OL,17,Fdigital spaces with properly preparing
OL,18,Ftheir children for a technological
OL,19,Ffuture.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1782917279
OL,3,CDigital and AI expert says changing
OL,4,Ccultural norms starts with social
OL,5,Cmedia ban
OL,7,F"It's about discussing this balance
OL,8,Fbetween AI tools that de-skill our
OL,9,Fyoung people and strip away at their
OL,10,Fsocial, emotional, and cognitive
OL,11,Fskills - and critically thinking about
OL,12,Fhow these technologies work so that we
OL,13,Fcan thrive in the future", she
OL,14,Fexplains.
OL,16,FShe adds there are ways of integrating
OL,17,Fdigital technologies throughout
OL,18,Fchildhood that don't take away
OL,19,Fchildren's abilities to think for
OL,20,Fthemselves or lead them to negative
OL,21,Fonline spaces.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1782917279
OL,3,CDigital and AI expert says changing
OL,4,Ccultural norms starts with social
OL,5,Cmedia ban
OL,7,FHer suggestions for parents include:
OL,9,F"We're thinking about quality over
OL,10,Fquantity", Dr Regehr explains.
OL,12,F"We really want to be distinguishing
OL,13,Fbetween regulated spaces and
OL,14,Falgorithmically-offered feeds":
OL,15,Fsomething she says the social media
OL,16,Fban could be the first step towards.
OL,18,FHowever, whilst she acknowledges it is
OL,19,Fa complex landscape, Dr Regehr remains
OL,20,Foptimistic that lasting change will be
OL,21,Fcreated.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
